        <num>CC 493.1</num>
        <heading>493.1.  Ownership of component parts</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 493.1.  Ownership of component parts
Things incorporated in or attached to an immovable so as to become its component parts under Articles 465 and 466 belong to the owner of the immovable.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110673</p>
